summary: Towel - Tier is now taking commissions!! Hi my name is MK and I’m an artist, and I’m taking commissions!!! I’m currently using...
caption:
Towel - Tier is now taking commissions!!

Hi my name is MK and I’m an artist, and I’m taking commissions!!! I’m currently using commissions to give me a lil extra money to support myself and afford my medications and medical junk, which is a lot right now. I may even stream while doing these commissions! Fun junk!

PRICING:

  • Basic Sketch - $10
  • Colored Sketch - $15
  • Lineart - $20
  • Full art - flat colors - $40
  • Full art - full color - $50
  • Extra character prices (anything above 1 character) will be dependent on designs and complexity.

What I won’t draw:

  • NSFW
  • Super Complicated Designs
  • Some Gore (I refuse to draw eye gore, unless it’s pastel others will have to be talked about before I do em.)
  • Animals (I give exception to anthro/furry!)
  • Mechs

Things I’m not the best at:

  • Masculine figures
  • Some anthro designs
  • Armor

If you’d like a commission please contact me here, my DeviantART (MKGPro) or my email! toweltierarts@gmail.com.

Slots:

  1. Closed
  2. Open
  3. Open
  4. Open

I reserve the right to to turn down any commissions I don’t think I can do! If I think I can do it, I certainly will!!
